tour. we could do a small tour.

850
00:48:18.458 --> 00:48:19.916
Round my place.

851
00:48:21.041 --> 00:48:22.291
Your place?

852
00:48:23.541 --> 00:48:25.541
-You have a place?
-I do.

853
00:48:26.625 --> 00:48:27.625
Wow.

854
00:48:28.375 --> 00:48:30.917
