-Oxford!
-Whoo-hoo!

908
00:51:38.750 --> 00:51:40.375
<i>♪ So kind</i>

909
00:51:40.458 --> 00:51:44.042
<i>♪ So long. dance on ♪</i>

910
00:51:44.125 --> 00:51:47.375
<i>♪ She's gone. dance on... ♪</i>

911
00:51:53.916 --> 00:51:55.750
