[Anna] His thesis is
important. I get it.

920
00:52:30.708 --> 00:52:34.125
-Laura! Hey.
-Hey! Nice turnout.

921
00:52:34.208 --> 00:52:36.167
Yeah. it seems like
everyone is here.

922
