951
00:53:58.833 --> 00:54:00.458
-Bollocks to this.
-[Charlie groans]

952
00:54:00.541 --> 00:54:02.250
-Bo... bollocks? Bollocks.
-[Maggie] Yeah.

953
00:54:02.333 --> 00:54:03.750
Bollocks to this!

